{"tid":1612958,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB「TVBuddy」疑屬僭建物 網民去信屋宇署投訴","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:05:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0235af0b7b7993e69937e95dbccbefdcdd9b47","tid":1612958,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】不少網民在反修訂《逃犯條例》風波中，不滿無綫新聞的報道手法，曾發起「追星運動」狙擊無綫舉辦及旗下藝人出席的活動。日前傳出無綫11月台慶亮燈儀式及節目巡禮，都可能取消或改形式進行。<br />\n<br />\n前晚有名為「專業清算師」的facebook帳號，以標題「我哋專業清算師要拆你TVB生招牌呀！」發文，說無綫位於將軍澳電視城大門上的官方吉祥物「TVBuddy」為僭建物，已去信屋宇署投訴，並展示一封署名「建築事務監督」的回信，內容說上址職員進出大樓的天台有僭建物，會向有關業主發出清拆令。就此事向無綫企業傳訊部查詢，但至截稿前仍未有任何回覆。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20191002/s00016/1569955633908/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20191002%2Fs00016%2F1569955633908%2F&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmqjPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=d06d0017\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20191002%2Fs00016%2F1569955633908%2F&h=f82cd897\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20191002/s00016/1569955633908/</a>"},{"pid":"03f9cf066bf24fa2b27ba5e92dc499fe4428e2a4","tid":1612958,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"@改名blind9"},{"pid":"0d46195c5597a8bf37e1dc621bb183858e4f25da","tid":1612958,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd73ea2f9dd18d6bb519e40bbffeda77555bcd3","tid":1612958,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{